@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> @DateTime.Now.ToString("dd MMM yyyy")</p>

    <p>
        Thank you for using our Job Portal. We are committed to protecting your personal information 
        and your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard the data 
        you provide when using our platform.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> name, email, phone number, address, resume, profile details.</li>
        <li><strong>Automatically Collected Data:</strong> IP address, device details, browser type, usage patterns.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To create and manage your account</li>
        <li>To process job applications</li>
        <li>To improve our services and user experience</li>
        <li>To send notifications and job-related updates</li>
        <li>To maintain platform security</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">3. How We Share Your Information</h4>
    <p>We may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Employers or recruiters when you apply for jobs</li>
        <li>Service providers that help operate our platform</li>
        <li>Law enforcement when required by law</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">4. Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        We use encryption, secure storage, and access controls to protect your data. 
        While we strive to ensure your information remains safe, no system is completely secure.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>You may request:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access to your data</li>
        <li>Correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Deletion of your account and associated records</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">6. Cookies</h4>
    <p>
        We use cookies to improve user experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, 
        but some features may not function properly.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">7. Updates to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Updates will be posted here with an 
        updated revision date.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">8. Contact Us</h4>
    <p>
        If you have questions, please contact us:<br />
        <strong>Email:</strong> support@joboria.com<br />
        <strong>Phone:</strong> +60 12-345 6789 
    </p>
</div>
